txt.en: Your mission is to reach the Ekhamâti camp where they are holding prisoners and free any that you can. Then put an end to the executioner before he can harm any more people.

'There is an urgent matter that is in need of your skills, [placeholder].\n\n'We have discovered a camp where prisoners are being held awaiting execution. I beg of you to go there now and save as many as you can. Be sure to put an end to the executioner himself to stop his terror.'
Your mission is to reach the Ekhamâti camp where they are holding prisoners and free any you can. Then put an end to the executioner before he can harm any more people.

'Your return is most welcome, and the prisoners you freed are being tended to now. They owe you their lives.\n\n'I thank you for your help and for stopping the executioner from doing any further harm to our people.'
There is no twist in this mission.
